# Credentials & sessions are configured — proceed without asking

The maintainer's machine already has working credentials. **Do not ask the user to set
these up or confirm them before running** `scrape`, `training`, `marathon-report`,
`pull-intake`, or `publish-sheet`. Assume configured and run the command.

- **Strava:** logged in via Playwright `storage_state` under `auth/` (`feeds/strava/session.py`).
